SUBENT        M0727001   20260411   20260518   20260518       M145
BIB                 11         27
TITLE      Cross sections for gamma-ray absorption by 19F, 24Mg
            and 40Ca in the 10 to 30 MeV region.
AUTHOR     (B.S.Dolbilkin,V.A.Zapevalov,V.I.Korin,L.E.Lazareva,
            F.A.Nikolaev)
INSTITUTE  (4RUSLEB)
REFERENCE  (J,BAS,30,354,1966)
            English translation of IZV,30,349,1966.
           (J,IZV,30,349,1966)
INC-SOURCE (BRST)
FACILITY   (SYNCH,4RUSLEB)
METHOD     (EXTB)
DETECTOR   (BPAIR) Magnetic pair spectrometer.
ANALYSIS   Photoabsorption cross   section   was   obtained   by
            subtraction of the atomic absorption  cross  section
            from  the  experimentally measured sum of atomic and
            nuclear absorption cross section.
           K.Siegbahn. Beta- and gamma-spectroscopy.
            Gostekhizdat,  Moscow, 1959. Atomic absorption cross
            section.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Mean-root-square errors.
HISTORY    (20071129C) Data were compiled at the Russia MSU SINP
            CDFE by V.Varlamov.
           (20140722A) Corrected  by  V.Varlamov:   REFERENCE,
            STATUS.
           (20150806A) Corrected by V.Varlamov: typo in ANALYSIS
           (20260411A) Corrected by V.Varlamov: TITLE,
            REFERENCE, REACTION, STATUS.
ENDBIB              27
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           30
